properties.Name: EmployeePhysicalCharacteristic

Columns.Name: EmployeeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Employee.

Columns.Name: PhysicalCharacteristicId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a physical characteristic.

Columns.Name: Timestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the associated information is reported, recorded or effective as-of.

Columns.Name: EmployeePhysicalCharacteristicNumber
Columns.Description:
The numeric parameter associated with the biometric.

Ex:

Weight = 175
Height = 5'10"

Columns.Name: EmployeePhysicalCharacteristicValue
Columns.Description:
The non-numeric parameter associated with the biometric.

Ex:
Eye color = blue

Columns.Name: EmployeePhysicalCharacteristicNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the employee physical characteristic.
